Submitted October 28, 2015, affirmed December 14, 2016, petition for review denied March 23, 2017 (361 Or 240) STATE OF OREGON, Plaintiff-Respondent, v. DONNA MARIE PATTON, Defendant-Appellant.

Klamath County Circuit Court

1200459CR; A156370 385 P3d 88 Peter Gartlan, Chief Defender, and Kyle Krohn, Deputy Public Defender, Office of Public Defense Services, filed the brief for appellant. Ellen F.
